overview: Recorded at the legendary Troubadour Club in West Hollywood, Los Angeles on the 2nd June 2000. Beginning with an introduction from legendary KROQ DJ Rodney Bigenheimer, the DVD includes 6 of their ten top 40 hits: 'Fill Her Up', 'As Good As It Gets', 'Speak To Me Someone', 'Where Are They Now?', 'For The Dead', 'Olympian') and some rarely heard gems.
title: Gene: Rising For Sunset
